Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.71,0:00:07.53,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, Noelle, and Magna encountered
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:11.07,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,a mysterious enemy when they \Narrived at Saussy Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.81,0:00:16.76,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,They fought hard against the enemy's \Nattack in order to protect the villagers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:19.87,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,but the enemy's magical powers \Nwere just too great.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:24.47,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,Not only can you negate magic,\Nyou can repel it, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:27.94,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,But that is not enough to defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:31.38,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,The blades of ice will \Ncome one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:33.72,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,Now, just try and protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:37.39,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.91,0:00:41.14,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to take everything Asta \Nand I have to protect the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.57,0:00:44.89,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, my powers \Nare reaching their limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.45,0:00:48.79,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,This turned out to be one hell \Nof a first mission for those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:50.90,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:55.42,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,But if I cut and run now, I'm not a real man!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.06,0:01:00.74,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,It just so happens I'm a lowly \Ncommoner myself! I'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.74,0:01:04.80,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... royalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.80,0:01:07.67,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I have more magical power \Nthan anyone else here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:09.59,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Step back, Lady Noe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:12.34,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,And yet I'm just holding them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.89,0:01:16.05,main,Lu,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Magic Knight...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:20.30,main,Lu,0000,0000,0000,,Save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.66,0:01:25.56,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,This little girl is asking for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:28.29,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to protect them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:30.57,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:31.79,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I can run now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:36.57,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A new spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.27,0:01:42.12,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea Dragon's Lair!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:51.59,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,As their owners mature, new spells \Nare engraved into the grimoires.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:56.57,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Maturity can stem from the wizard's \Nmagical powers growing through training,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.57,0:01:59.32,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,or improving the creativity \Nof their magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:02.35,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes, it can come \Nfrom a rise or change
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:05.35,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,in their emotional state, \Nor gaining new resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.18,0:02:10.35,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect them! I'm royalty,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:13.94,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,and a member of the Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:40.30,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,750)}Those Who Protect
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:44.87,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Grey words can't make anything happen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:47.39,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, yeah I know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:52.79,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wishing to fly freely across the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:54.65,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I dreamed it all my life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:58.53,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Step by step I go, though \Nit's a doubtful world 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:00.68,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't care how much I fall
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:04.10,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Instinct is my guide, I never give up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:10.29,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To faraway future, I burst out running
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:15.46,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Go beyond even the unseen fears
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:20.84,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The vision I had, so I can be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:26.10,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday I will write the next page
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:29.60,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my hope
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.54,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that page from someday
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:34.69,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:37.65,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I call this a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:54.09,main,Lu,0000,0000,0000,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:05.34,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I guess you're not so tough after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:08.29,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:12.35,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lady Noe! What'd I tell you?\NYou can do it if you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:16.36,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,What? What is this magical power?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:22.91,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The beast had been waiting for \Nhis chance to fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:26.87,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,For the moment when he could sink his teeth
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:28.79,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,into his prey's throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:31.79,flashback,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,The three of you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:35.62,flashback,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,also had enough magical power to \Njoin the Magic Knights, did you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:38.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any magical powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:42.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm going to kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:49.14,main,Dejire & Gustave,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Heath!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:51.18,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Stupidsta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:54.14,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He... He did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:03.65,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He broke my momentum by \Nmaking me slip on a patch of ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:07.13,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,Though your sword can negate magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:10.66,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,it appears that you're just \Na normal human after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.79,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:33.58,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,May you sleep... for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:36.89,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,A-Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:40.25,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,That spell possesses \Nimmense magical power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:44.40,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,But it's only a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:49.00,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,I should be able to create an \Nentrance big enough for one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:56.85,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,It should take about 25 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:04.15,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,You lot seem to greatly enjoy wasting my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:06.86,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,You will pay a heavy price for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:13.68,italics,Manga,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have much power left, \Nbut I have to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:18.85,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Fire and ice. In terms of magical \Nattributes, I have the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:24.03,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,But he has enough magical power \Nto turn that advantage around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:27.19,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,He's just too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:30.07,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Mister Yami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:34.12,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'm going to win against...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:35.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:37.00,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.58,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:43.95,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:46.63,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite resilient. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:50.01,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to swing \Nthat sword with those wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:55.85,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,You're no wild boar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:10.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:17.58,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,Stop. Don't make me waste any more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:22.33,flashback,Magna's friend A,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Magna!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:30.38,flashback,Magna's friend B,0000,0000,0000,,To think that someone from Rayaka \Nwould end up being a Magic Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:32.67,flashback,Manga's friend d,0000,0000,0000,,You're the pride of our village!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:34.47,flashback,Magna's friend A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's lift him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:37.25,flashback,Magna's friends,0000,0000,0000,,Magna!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:39.40,flashback,Magna's friends,0000,0000,0000,,Magna!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:41.64,flashback,Magna's friends,0000,0000,0000,,Magna!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:47.90,flashback,Seyhe,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's wonderful. Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.53,flashback,Seyhe,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Magna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:50.94,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:54.36,flashback,Seyhe,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're more than just a delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.54,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:00.37,flashback,Seyhe,0000,0000,0000,,This is from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:02.37,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Old Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:08.38,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:13.63,flashback,Seyhe,0000,0000,0000,,It looks good on you.\NBecome the best man you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:15.33,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:22.64,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to give up until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:29.14,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What good would it do if I gave up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:34.50,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,This spell... It's probably a lot easier \Nto get outside than in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.50,0:08:36.65,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Yes, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:39.66,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving the villagers to you, Lady Noe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:42.16,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:47.67,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,You have no chance of winning. \NWhy won't you give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:51.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If I give up, who's going to protect them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:08:55.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I've realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:09:00.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just because of our promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:03.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become the Wizard King
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:05.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,so I can protect everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:09.94,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King? What a foolish dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:13.94,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, you'll be dead in one minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:16.95,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,That's not happening, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:22.95,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to kill him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:28.46,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,you're going to have to get \Nthrough me, his senior, first!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:30.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Magna!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:36.09,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You know... You're quite the man, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:40.59,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,You fool. You've just hastened your death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.59,0:09:42.10,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:45.39,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:47.89,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:49.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:51.11,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Time for an initiation!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:58.36,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! My last remaining bit of magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:05.29,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:11.57,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Magic: Prison Death Scattershot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:18.63,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,So this is your final spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:21.10,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,How wasteful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:25.10,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:33.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:36.70,italics,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,They drew us in with a decoy, \Nthen used our blind spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.28,italics,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,Magic reflection!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:43.53,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:52.49,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better thank me,\Nyou mohawked delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:55.88,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes! I was able to control my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:59.34,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You never shut up, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:06.35,italics,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,These flames... won't go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:08.54,italics,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just freeze them over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:12.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:17.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can still move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:19.11,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:23.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:42.85,italics,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,These flames... won't go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:44.99,italics,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just freeze them over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:49.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:53.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can still move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:55.61,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.01,0:12:00.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:04.53,italics,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.21,0:12:07.28,italics,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:10.34,italics,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,lost to this brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:17.04,italics,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted... to be of more use...\Nto the master...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:24.05,main,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,They did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:26.03,main,Lu,0000,0000,0000,,Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:29.97,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We beat him for sure this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:44.14,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,First, my Flame Magic: \NPrison Death Scattershot,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.14,0:12:49.33,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,and now, Flame Binding Magic: \NFlame Bondage Formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:54.03,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're more talented \Nthan you look. Have some praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:56.02,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'm your senior!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:58.37,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking down on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:13:00.34,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're physically below—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:01.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Magna!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:12.03,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! You need \Nto follow through properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:18.38,main,Lu,0000,0000,0000,,So cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:21.65,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You've still got a ways to go, Lady Noe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:26.24,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, it looks like one got away.\NUgh, I blew it! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:39.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you like that?\NSome lowly commoners just won.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:47.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you like that, damn it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:49.79,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:54.89,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, he's asleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:59.15,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, he's so ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:04.15,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He's stupid, loud, and a lowly commoner...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:07.66,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But he's sort of amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:13.17,main,Villager A,0000,0000,0000,,Whew... We're saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:15.33,main,Villager B,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:18.16,main,Villager C,0000,0000,0000,,Is he really a commoner like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:21.67,main,Villager D,0000,0000,0000,,Magna, young lady... Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:24.13,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:25.92,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:28.89,main,Villager A,0000,0000,0000,,You're our saviors!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:36.39,main,Villager A,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? An anti-bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:16.85,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You finally awake, you jerk?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:20.18,main,Manga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to rest a bit more \Nand then escort you to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:23.21,main,Manga,0000,0000,0000,,the royal capital on my Crazy Cyclone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:32.36,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Spend the rest of your life atoning for what \Nyou did to those villagers, you bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:36.87,italics,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,So my magic is sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:41.03,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to spill everything \Nto the Magic Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:45.13,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,including who you guys are \Nand what your motives are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:46.11,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:49.41,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,It appears the end has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:56.85,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,There was a magic item inside him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:59.85,main,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Magic: Ice Burial.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:03.35,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:17.95,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about resolve. Is there \Nsomeone he was that loyal to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:23.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:29.67,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,He went through all that... \NWhat was he after, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:32.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What do...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:36.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think life is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:41.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never going to acknowledge these jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:44.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:17:00.33,main,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:03.82,main,Lu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:08.84,main,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa really loved the view from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.22,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:13.13,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,So, Nick, I heard
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:18.60,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,that Old Man Seihi was the only \None to stand up to those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:47.70,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Your grandpa was a real man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:51.85,main,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa sounded really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:54.05,main,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,He said that even though it was
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:56.82,main,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,just gambling, he still\Nbeat some Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:57.84,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:01.57,main,Lu,0000,0000,0000,,He gave this to me as a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:05.25,main,Lu,0000,0000,0000,,He even bought lots of yummy \Nfood for everyone in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.18,0:18:16.74,main,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,He never got to be one, but Grandpa \Nalways admired the Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:18.49,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:21.70,main,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,And they were also his regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:23.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Regret?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:28.78,main,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,He always regretted not working \Nharder when he was younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.27,0:18:30.33,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:36.18,main,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,But... he seemed really \Nhappy about the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:38.84,main,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,Magna was working hard for the both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:41.59,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:48.35,main,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you think... I'll be able \Nto become a Magic Knight, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:50.10,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:54.46,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:58.32,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Your future is something that \Nyou decide for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:03.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not only am I a commoner, but I've got\Nno magic powers, and I still made it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:07.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But you've gotta work super extra hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:10.03,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Give it your all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:11.29,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:13.29,main,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:16.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,By the time you join the Magic Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:19.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be working even harder,\Ndoing even more missions,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:22.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll be even closer to \Nbecoming the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:25.56,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. There you go talking nonsense again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:29.81,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,But you need to dream big.\NThat's what it means to be a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:35.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:37.03,main,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:38.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:47.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:52.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What do you have against my head, \Nyou stupid bird?! You wanna fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:54.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:19:59.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's that stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:03.68,main,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's a charm that my grandpa had.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:06.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's really important!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:10.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:16.34,main,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,You can have it.\NApparently that bird really likes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:18.73,main,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,It's the least I can do to \Nrepay you guys for saving us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.29,0:20:21.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:26.10,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Those spiteful little eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:30.50,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.38,0:20:33.29,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You can come over here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.39,0:20:38.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:42.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What is your problem with my head?!\NI'm gonna barbecue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:44.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:49.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:51.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The heck are you doing, you jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:13.03,main,Shadow,0000,0000,0000,,So Heath was... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:17.06,main,Shadow,0000,0000,0000,,So the magic stone fell into \Nthe hands of the Black Bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:18.54,main,Dejire,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:21.46,main,Shadow,0000,0000,0000,,No matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:25.45,main,Shadow,0000,0000,0000,,We can take care of the \NBlack Bulls at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:28.92,main,Shadow,0000,0000,0000,,Let them hold on to the \Nmagic stone for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.17,0:21:37.81,main,Shadow,0000,0000,0000,,Our master's resurrection is close at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:59.09,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can escape from here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:05.84,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again in the small closed off classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.16,0:22:13.60,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The star of the class was shining yet again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.25,0:22:20.61,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,They shine so bright that I close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.12,0:22:23.48,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought many times
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.88,0:22:27.20,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That the revolution was within my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.20,0:22:34.66,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it strange? If you want \Nto laugh, go ahead and laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.02,0:22:41.63,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of us who were left \Nbehind wanted to become something
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.63,0:22:48.88,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We repeat the same morning over and over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:55.77,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who \Ncan choose your tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:23:00.97,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go beyond our current selves
