Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.29,0:23:19.05,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.79,0:23:22.79,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(526,1)}Who's the Most Similar?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.90,0:23:22.79,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the Most Similar?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.13,0:23:29.66,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The winner is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.19,0:23:32.80,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,this bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.13,0:23:37.50,main,Three,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.46,0:23:41.35,main,Old man,0000,0000,0000,,Magna, you've grown so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.35,0:23:44.11,main,Old man,0000,0000,0000,,You're no longer just a delinquent. \NYou're a real man now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.11,0:23:46.52,main,Old man,0000,0000,0000,,You're on fire! You're shining!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.52,0:23:48.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 11:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.57,0:23:55.00,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 11\N\N{\fs18}What Happened on a Certain Day in the Castle Town
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.53,0:23:50.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,"What Happened on a Certain \NDay in the Castle Town."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.90,0:23:53.70,main,old,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up is my magic!
